snippet.title: Female Running Back Makes History in Pro Football Game

localized.description:
Jennifer Welter is the first female to play in a men's professional football game as a running back. She got 3 carries in the red zone for a total of -1 yards. Her stat line may not be eye popping but her tenacity sure is. Patrick Jones (@Patrick_E_Jones) has the rest.
